          <msContents>
            <summary>Treatise on the theory of music, including division of frets, ratio of intervals, consonance and dissonance, cycles, rhythmic and melodic modes, and the 5-string oud or lute.</summary>
            <textLang mainLang="ara">Arabic</textLang>
            <msItem>
              <title>Kitāb al-Adwār fī al-mūsīqá.</title>
              <title type="vernacular">كتاب الادوار في الموسيقى</title>
              <author>
